<n:h3 id="input-groups-buttons">Button addons</n:h3>
<n:p><![CDATA[Buttons in input groups are a bit different and require one extra level of nesting. Instead of <code>.input-group-addon</code>, you'll need to use <code>.input-group-btn</code> to wrap the buttons. This is required due to default browser styles that cannot be overridden.]]></n:p>
	<div class="bs-example">
		<div class="row">
			<div class="col-lg-6">
				<div class="input-group">
					<span class="input-group-btn">
						<button>
							Go!
						</button>
					</span>
					<textbox class="form-control"/>
				</div><!-- /input-group -->
			</div><!-- /.col-lg-6 -->
			<div class="col-lg-6">
				<div class="input-group">
					<textbox class="form-control"/>
					<span class="input-group-btn">
						<button>
							Go!
						</button>
					</span>
				</div><!-- /input-group -->
			</div><!-- /.col-lg-6 -->
		</div><!-- /.row -->
	</div>
	
